{"tid":2313312,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"組媽好似鍾意我 聖誕唔洗自己一個人過了","createTime":"2020-12-05T16:23:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-05T17:24:12.000Z","uid":366192,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"18a6e50de395187daa287f8c7f4690ac8922fc1b","tid":2313312,"uid":366192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T16:23:30.000Z","msg":"最近就到sem尾<br />\n又多assignment  又有考試<br />\n咁我讀緊電競系 要日日打機<br />\n點知今日組媽比咗張紙仔我 叫我比心機 右下角仲有粒心心❤️❤️<br />\n果一刻我就知道佢對我有意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />始終我都算係個準職業選手<br />\n之後我即刻自信大增 一日內LOL由銀牌升上金牌<br />\n哈哈 等我聖誕節果日同佢講我LOL有金牌<br />\n到時佢肯定會迷上我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n進度十分良好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae3c3a65f2def699e42d9e44628886d290da0df6","tid":2313312,"uid":366192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T16:24:53.000Z","msg":"葡萄我的人只會默默留下負評便離去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ff51c6fe71360674039ab5466944f37e0d03b67","tid":2313312,"uid":371558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T16:24:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6b90fdd781a4373097f07841427fd6daef4f5582","tid":2313312,"uid":135081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T16:25:14.000Z","msg":"傻仔 咁都唔即刻抱起佢屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢依家搵咗我了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa5d1714bafb343bfcaa6f67b3550ef28504c123","tid":2313312,"uid":366655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T16:32:36.000Z","msg":"組媽：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mJyshyG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmJyshyG.jpg&h=8a00c94e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7dd7378b08db98ead22716d070a2c17a1527d6f8","tid":2313312,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-1